    "originContent": "### Manual install (legacy)",
    "translatedContent": "### 手动安装（传统方式）"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "7d6ZW2ktGTS+XVJavSu2BYZdI9MfSuoBp0Yjzl10zoQ=",
    "originContent": "To install, use the provided `Makefile`:",
    "translatedContent": "要安装，请使用提供的 `Makefile`："
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "ivgYKrHo9QnPgZYRA645sKpipVpw39MbuUN0CN9LfCA=",
    "originContent": "```sh",
    "translatedContent": "```sh"
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "Elnm9OFx6gQ5o+fCizO9AqnZlmibpbRMTwADriGZcCY=",
    "originContent": "git clone https://github.com/saysjonathan/dwm.tmux.git",
    "translatedContent": "git clone https://github.com/saysjonathan/dwm.tmux.git"
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "8ZlQXbwLGYe0TQzzmVO9073g6WW5G2hzNoZSOVLHCNM=",
    "originContent": "cd dwm.tmux",
    "translatedContent": "cd dwm.tmux"
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "0FqioV+zxA7+6wO+xEU5PwAHRITPAcj7LakMpmlaVTE=",
    "originContent": "make",
    "translatedContent": "make"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "默认情况下，`dwm.tmux` 使用 `/usr/local` 作为其前缀。要更改前缀："
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "rc/TFKChfniVlal46YFUQ8n435MUOQCV0ahSqBe37ek=",
    "originContent": "By default `dwm.tmux` uses `/usr/local` as its prefix. To change the prefix:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "ivgYKrHo9QnPgZYRA645sKpipVpw39MbuUN0CN9LfCA=",
    "originContent": "```sh",
    "translatedContent": "```sh"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "bJSCDZa+MhVEZ+dbxk3d8sehjsJyF6fxUz1ksq0KyBw=",
    "originContent": "make PREFIX=$HOME",
    "translatedContent": "make PREFIX=$HOME"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "Crubxh7qAAued2XyX/J25OW7MPlAq+s1E35tHA6hMGE=",
    "originContent": "Ensure that `$PREFIX/bin` is in your `PATH`.",
    "translatedContent": "确保 `$PREFIX/bin` 在你的 `PATH` 中。"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "2G+RXNYmFng7SDlLcfx21ULzFygjnVtlj+g/uwj0rV4=",
    "originContent": "To use, source the `dwm.tmux` tmux config:",
    "translatedContent": "要使用，请加载 `dwm.tmux` tmux 配置："
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "ivgYKrHo9QnPgZYRA645sKpipVpw39MbuUN0CN9LfCA=",
    "originContent": "```sh",
    "translatedContent": "```sh"
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "R4xApo8E3THEC4lXaD4myHlbyO+zFIF3EOM7jZgrVg0=",
    "originContent": "echo 'source-file /usr/local/lib/dwm.tmux' >> $HOME/.tmux.conf",
    "translatedContent": "echo 'source-file /usr/local/lib/dwm.tmux' >> $HOME/.tmux.conf"
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## 使用方法"
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "Y7/WGgVhslWiyqCi463Qkcp+Mn8voGpAfLsv80G4WNg=",
    "originContent": "## Usage",
    "translatedContent": "`dwm.tmux` 定义了以下命令别名，每个都有默认快捷键绑定："
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "OlhWkeTHXPh7fIc8wfUZ9IBMIdYfFPhMKXfSqiTmRIw=",
    "originContent": "`dwm.tmux` defines the following command aliases, each with a default keybinding:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "- `newpane` `Meta-n` 创建一个新窗格并将其放置在主窗格中"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "bC6ZO6bW/cCZu25f3U9wYXwEAg1qX92nrv9gZeqlL+U=",
    "originContent": "- `newpane` `Meta-n` Create a new pane and place it in the Main pane",
    "translatedContent": "- `newpanecurdir` `Meta-w` 创建一个新窗格，起始目录与当前相同，并将其放置在主窗格中"
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "7ESFAcrChhOHt9T6t6onidmaqiyTB0lcaLPae7i2jhg=",
    "originContent": "- `newpanecurdir` `Meta-w` Create a new pane starting in the same directory and place it in the Main pane",
    "translatedContent": "- `killpane` `Meta-c` 关闭当前窗格。如果该窗格是主窗格，则关闭该窗格并将堆栈中的第一个窗格提升为主窗格"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "G4bbr4cbrXnCHU3EKFJC3i7NPMzthNXAPpE0tOb+wEQ=",
    "originContent": "- `killpane` `Meta-c` Close the current pane. If the pane is in the Main pane, close the pane and promote the first pane in the stack to the Main pane",
    "translatedContent": "- `movepane[0-9]` `Meta-Shift-[0-9]` 将当前窗格移动到指定窗口"
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "8W1J3vBNdKHDRB+6ZjCz3X2TD9eBJS4Avkc6LVf6eE4=",
    "originContent": "- `movepane[0-9]` `Meta-Shift-[0-9]` Move the current pane to the specified window",
    "translatedContent": "- `nextpane` `Meta-j` 选择下一个窗格（顺时针）；在单片模式下交换全屏窗格"
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "iCEUFkQ7R4OuvqK2XQ5+0mArvnQICfOXQM8jWymDErA=",
    "originContent": "- `nextpane` `Meta-j` Select the next pane (clockwise); swaps fullscreen pane in monocle mode",
    "translatedContent": "- `prevpane` `Meta-k` 选择上一个窗格（逆时针）；在单片模式下交换全屏窗格"
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "3IJklbZz3hyb9Sf2x15NzmK7jZO/9ej0RZaURnjCCKo=",
    "originContent": "- `prevpane` `Meta-k` Select the previous pane (counterclockwise); swaps fullscreen pane in monocle mode",
    "translatedContent": "- `stackup` `Meta-J` 将聚焦窗格向上移动堆栈"
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "I+KTFUiA5/Gp+DtIO/OeIo/IVL8ApAUrflhTfZeD/oU=",
    "originContent": "- `stackup` `Meta-J` Move focused pane up the stack",
    "translatedContent": "- `stackdown` `Meta-K` 将聚焦窗格向下移动堆栈"
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "wG/wUtvwtnCJPGuwwbKQSneqNkNsbDhYOJDW8OmksHY=",
    "originContent": "- `stackdown` `Meta-K` Move focused pane down the stack",
    "translatedContent": "- `rotateccw` `Meta-<` 逆时针旋转窗格"
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "k3YGXJuwQv0r97DJ0XphgfwOzRBqUh0qHo1kvGWv+9g=",
    "originContent": "- `rotateccw` `Meta-<` Rotate panes counterclockwise",
    "translatedContent": "- `rotatecw` `Meta->` 顺时针旋转窗格"
  },
  {
    "row": 55,
    "rowsha": "IkAr1NhWxEMr4avIlBwDIh/fnp0TPHiFam5NvrFpiC4=",
    "originContent": "- `rotatecw` `Meta->` Rotate panes clockwise",
    "translatedContent": "- `tile` `Meta-t` 返回平铺布局，退出单片模式（如果激活）"
  },
  {
    "row": 56,
    "rowsha": "gfTx9GkearPbwGLAPlBDpown4UIwBHH0+zrkUOaDDfQ=",
    "originContent": "- `tile` `Meta-t` Return to tiled layout, exiting monocle if active",
    "translatedContent": "- `monocle` `Meta-Space` 切换单片模式（当前窗格全屏）"
  },
  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "e8VmYDZMbfniwxyI7Co9a7hOwccN8QoBByyTo3T6iFU=",
    "originContent": "- `monocle` `Meta-Space` Toggle monocle mode (fullscreen current pane)",
    "translatedContent": "- `zoom` `Meta-Enter` 将选中窗格放置到主窗格中"
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "AWkY2sCBbnUZRD/os6KcKs8BuPJQn6BXbltdmUzikZA=",
    "originContent": "- `zoom` `Meta-Enter` Place selected pane in the Main pane",
    "translatedContent": "- `decmfact` `Meta-h` 减小主窗格空间因子"
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "F1ZM3KlpBjNUBjfCZhm/caU9YcVwYt85wcyLQvmf/FU=",
    "originContent": "- `decmfact` `Meta-h` Decrease the main pane space factor",
    "translatedContent": "- `incmfact` `Meta-l` 增大主窗格空间因子"
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "t4RIe2b8pox3ODQC2xBSRyW0VQ6DW5sCbmN+bkCntbA=",
    "originContent": "- `incmfact` `Meta-l` Increase the main pane space factor",
    "translatedContent": "- `window[0-9]` `Meta-[0-9]` 按 ID 选择目标窗口"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "jUBDhiDs5XeodTefg2eVlySLY47tR8U+ZvVB25P/aUk=",
    "originContent": "- `window[0-9]` `Meta-[0-9]` Select the target window by ID",
    "translatedContent": "- `newwindow` `Meta-N` 创建一个新窗口，起始目录与当前窗格相同"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "jUn9ddOsTMQ6o97RQCp54GHIl/aSQOP2qL1uJoA959w=",
    "originContent": "- `newwindow` `Meta-N` Create a new window starting in the same directory as the current pane",
    "translatedContent": "- `killwindow` `Meta-X` 删除当前活动窗口"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "OsC6hIo0Veh2jnOjjfKE+Y7sjrJ/YJZfGepFarwmjmY=",
    "originContent": "- `killwindow` `Meta-X` Delete the current active window",
    "translatedContent": "- `popup` `Meta-p` 在当前窗格目录下显示一个浮动窗格弹出窗口"
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "j85RAJUTkPRNHBS7nsIo3vBw6JBIUBct6KGm79qn4fk=",
    "originContent": "- `popup` `Meta-p` Display a floating pane popup in the current pane's directory",
    "translatedContent": "- `incpfact` `Meta-.` 相对于其他窗格，增加堆栈中聚焦窗格的大小"
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "du3JjJulIxMts57FDdzdqz1c0Wsm86jlFcg/zTMV5gI=",
    "originContent": "- `incpfact` `Meta-.` Increase the size of the focused pane in the stack, relative to the other panes",
    "translatedContent": "- `decpfact` `Meta-,` 相对于其他窗格，减少堆栈中聚焦窗格的大小"
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "UOgN2uiYQdxYETUuiMU9jWOt/NQEcLA0Z7I5kHfn9hA=",
    "originContent": "- `decpfact` `Meta-,` Decrease the size of the focused pane in the stack, relative to the other panes",
    "translatedContent": "- `resetpfact` `Meta-=` 重置聚焦窗格的 pfact"
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "qh4PfWmMP4IZQVuQ5TBWKeKTjZ1TPmxNzdJkOzhVLFk=",
    "originContent": "- `resetpfact` `Meta-=` Reset the pfact of the focused pane",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 68,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "还包括窗口切换的额外快捷键绑定："
  },
  {
    "row": 69,
    "rowsha": "nV97/x8ZYiV1WkhMe+9nUL07eLw3n2I6asubCjdcjrc=",
    "originContent": "Additional keybindings for window cycling are also included:",
    "translatedContent": "- `Meta-[` 上一个窗口"
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "3hh+Z7DRHwZqNuFD5sv8frmnGvSZ8OCKUXdgaWhuJMM=",
    "originContent": "- `Meta-[` Previous window",
    "translatedContent": "- `Meta-]` 下一个窗口"
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "xJYkqxQYX3NuMyIiq9u6Z0MchOoLKdDuugkcsWBENfo=",
    "originContent": "- `Meta-]` Next window",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "还定义了调整行为的全局选项："
  },
  {
    "row": 73,
    "rowsha": "zJBoGelO4vYvAUCdBznFQiSZ8YyoqSZ9+chKUet4cF0=",
    "originContent": "Also defined are global options to tweak behavior:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 74,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "- `mfact` 主窗格空间因子，主窗格大小占窗口总大小的百分比"
  },
  {
    "row": 75,
    "rowsha": "IdYcz20Ry2+5Map5fDXev0ifo+Yb5pBmUg4vLsAj/Qc=",
    "originContent": "- `mfact` Main pane space factor, the size of the main pane as a percentage of total window size",
    "translatedContent": "- `killlast` 如果值大于 `0`，即使是窗口中的最后一个窗格也会被关闭"
  },
  {
    "row": 76,
    "rowsha": "aSDe/nKLVYetSOGu/x7GWnmzV8owKMHjzCypjd2fXXo=",
    "originContent": "- `killlast` If value is greater than `0`, kill pane even if it is the last pane in a window",
    "translatedContent": "- `monocle` 跟踪活动布局模式；0 为平铺，1 为单片。自动设置，但可读取以检查当前状态"
  },
  {
    "row": 77,
    "rowsha": "2tZLKKrnrw85VRolLm8uwq2xf4HgNNHYrIxU1uA5tmk=",
    "originContent": "- `monocle` Tracks active layout mode; 0 for tile, 1 for monocle. Set automatically but can be read to inspect current state.",
    "translatedContent": "- `pfact` 每个窗格的堆栈大小因子，范围 1-9，默认 5。值越大，该窗格在堆栈中占用的相对高度越大"
  },
  {
    "row": 78,
    "rowsha": "8OwAZ11R+2vuDh1ouIkqT3V0yDeDNHZcJ/LLQnt15QU=",
